00:27:20,300 --> 00:27:21,660
Thinking too much.

587
00:27:24,220 --> 00:27:27,340
Prince Sui has taken over Mount Yang.

588
00:27:28,980 --> 00:27:30,340
This must be related

589
00:27:31,340 --> 00:27:33,820
to Sun Yun'er's demand for money

590
00:27:33,820 --> 00:27:35,100
from Liu Miantang.

591
00:27:36,860 --> 00:27:38,020
It's likely

592
00:27:38,860 --> 00:27:40,180
that they can't

593
00:27:40,180 --> 00:27:42,140
report the money to the court.

594
00:27:44,980 --> 00:27:46,180
I have a premonition

595
00:27:47,220 --> 00:27:48,700
that Prince Sui will

596
00:27:48,700 --> 00:27:50,060
stir up a storm in the court,

597
00:27:50,060 --> 00:27:52,220
and we will be implicated

598
00:27:52,860 --> 00:27:53,940
and lose control.

599
00:27:57,180 --> 00:27:58,980
And Liu Miantang.

600
00:28:00,100 --> 00:28:01,540
If she is related

601
00:28:01,540 --> 00:28:02,660
to this money,

602
00:28:03,380 --> 00:28:04,300
her situation will only

603
00:28:04,300 --> 00:28:05,900
become more dangerous.

604
00:28:09,060 --> 00:28:11,100
Lu Wen is strange.

605
00:28:12,340 --> 00:28:13,700
He allowed his concubine

606
00:28:13,700 --> 00:28:14,980
to manage the money.

607
00:28:16,060 --> 00:28:17,420
But now, Liu Miantang

608
00:28:17,420 --> 00:28:19,380
surely can't remember where the money is.

609
00:28:28,780 --> 00:28:29,820
Is there a problem?

610
00:28:30,420 --> 00:28:31,260
Yes.

611
00:28:33,700 --> 00:28:34,700
Cui Xingzhou.

612
00:28:35,540 --> 00:28:36,420
You've changed.

613
00:28:38,980 --> 00:28:39,860
In these years,

614
00:28:40,060 --> 00:28:42,060
with the young Emperor ascending the throne,

615
00:28:42,460 --> 00:28:44,740
you've spent your days drinking
and playing Go with me,

616
00:28:44,740 --> 00:28:45,700
seeing events unfold.

617
00:28:46,420 --> 00:28:48,460
When did you start saying things

618
00:28:48,460 --> 00:28:50,660
like you have no control over your actions?

619
00:28:51,740 --> 00:28:53,820
And when did you start to worry

620
00:28:54,060 --> 00:28:55,100
about being unable

621
00:28:55,100 --> 00:28:56,220
to protect someone?

622
00:28:58,140 --> 00:28:59,180
This time...

623
00:28:59,180 --> 00:29:00,780
You're concerned about someone.

624
00:29:02,480 --> 00:29:03,580
You've had a weakness.

625
00:29:14,660 --> 00:29:16,780
The crabapple flowers bloom beautifully,

626
00:29:18,300 --> 00:29:20,620
tall and graceful, with heavenly fragrance.

627
00:29:21,140 --> 00:29:23,300
Pick flowers while you can.

628
00:29:24,220 --> 00:29:25,100
What a pity.

629
00:29:26,500 --> 00:29:28,500
A lover brings a bottle,

630
00:29:29,300 --> 00:29:30,340
but the bottle

631
00:29:30,660 --> 00:29:32,100
contains the main flower.

632
00:29:32,620 --> 00:29:33,940
Enough of your rambling.

633
00:29:34,140 --> 00:29:35,500
I want to remind you

634
00:29:35,940 --> 00:29:37,180
not to forget tomorrow.

635
00:29:42,980 --> 00:29:43,820
Rest assured.

636
00:29:44,980 --> 00:29:45,860
I have a plan.

637
00:29:47,580 --> 00:29:49,100
Thank you for rescuing me.

638
00:29:50,500 --> 00:29:51,380
Yun'er.

639
00:29:52,700 --> 00:29:53,860
Do you realize your mistake?

640
00:29:55,020 --> 00:29:57,140
It was my impulsive action

641
00:29:57,660 --> 00:29:59,980
that led to this dangerous situation,

642
00:30:01,340 --> 00:30:02,900
causing worry for you.

643
00:30:03,020 --> 00:30:04,220
Utterly foolish.

644
00:30:05,620 --> 00:30:07,220
I've been in hiding for many years,

645
00:30:08,500 --> 00:30:09,820
acting meek and subservient

646
00:30:10,220 --> 00:30:12,060
to avoid attention.

647
00:30:13,580 --> 00:30:15,740
Today, you acted recklessly,

648
00:30:15,740 --> 00:30:16,980
blinded by personal grudges.

649
00:30:17,900 --> 00:30:19,980
Are you trying to ruin my major plans?

650
00:30:21,420 --> 00:30:22,700
You were to test others

651
00:30:23,420 --> 00:30:25,420
but got exposed.

652
00:30:27,460 --> 00:30:29,580
If it weren't for your hard work
and achievements,

653
00:30:30,700 --> 00:30:31,740
you'd die

654
00:30:33,100 --> 00:30:34,380
here in Zhenzhou.

655
00:30:35,380 --> 00:30:36,420
I've known my mistake.

656
00:30:44,540 --> 00:30:45,660
Don't you understand?

657
00:30:47,330 --> 00:30:48,420
Why would a lord

658
00:30:49,300 --> 00:30:51,460
care about your personal grudge

659
00:30:51,460 --> 00:30:52,780
with Liu Miantang?

660
00:30:57,380 --> 00:30:58,300
Could it be...?

661
00:30:58,820 --> 00:31:00,100
Cui Jiu

662
00:31:01,700 --> 00:31:03,380
is Cui Xingzhou.

663
00:31:07,300 --> 00:31:11,500
(Notice)

664
00:31:11,500 --> 00:31:12,980
Impersonating someone's husband

665
00:31:13,380 --> 00:31:14,280
to cheat money.

666
00:31:15,530 --> 00:31:16,520
Unheard of.

667
00:31:17,420 --> 00:31:18,500
How can there be such jerks

668
00:31:18,500 --> 00:31:19,700
impersonating husbands

669
00:31:19,940 --> 00:31:21,700
to extort money on the streets?

670
00:31:22,780 --> 00:31:24,980
- It's utterly scandalous.
- Such people who harm others

671
00:31:24,980 --> 00:31:26,190
should be arrested

672
00:31:26,190 --> 00:31:27,080
and interrogated.

673
00:31:28,940 --> 00:31:30,670
- Truly depraved, right?
- Yes.

674
00:31:38,100 --> 00:31:39,140
Madam.

675
00:31:40,780 --> 00:31:41,860
The wrongdoers

676
00:31:41,860 --> 00:31:43,620
have been detained by the authorities.

677
00:31:43,820 --> 00:31:45,820
After seeing the notice,

678
00:31:46,300 --> 00:31:48,140
why are you still frowning?

679
00:31:49,060 --> 00:31:50,420
In my view,

680
00:31:50,540 --> 00:31:52,140
Sun Yun'er's manner and appearance

681
00:31:52,140 --> 00:31:53,860
don't seem like those of a lowly person.

682
00:31:54,300 --> 00:31:55,860
Moreover, I always feel

683
00:31:55,940 --> 00:31:57,980
there is some connection between us.

684
00:31:59,300 --> 00:32:00,740
How could that be?

685
00:32:01,140 --> 00:32:02,660
How could you

686
00:32:02,660 --> 00:32:03,740
have any connection

687
00:32:03,740 --> 00:32:04,940
with such petty rats?

688
00:32:05,140 --> 00:32:06,140
Why did she address me

689
00:32:06,140 --> 00:32:07,700
as Miantang so intimately?

690
00:32:07,700 --> 00:32:08,540
Well.

691
00:32:09,140 --> 00:32:10,300
Perhaps

692
00:32:10,620 --> 00:32:12,620
she was trying to get close to you.

693
00:32:12,820 --> 00:32:14,260
And her gaze at me

694
00:32:14,260 --> 00:32:15,540
was filled with resentment.

695
00:32:16,780 --> 00:32:19,140
She must be jealous of your beauty.

696
00:32:19,660 --> 00:32:21,060
But when I looked at her,

697
00:32:21,380 --> 00:32:23,260
I also felt inexplicable anger.

698
00:32:23,540 --> 00:32:24,380
Because...

699
00:32:26,700 --> 00:32:28,660
Because...

700
00:32:28,660 --> 00:32:29,580
Nanny Li.

701
00:32:30,220 --> 00:32:31,300
You look guilty.

702
00:32:31,540 --> 00:32:32,860
Are you hiding something from me?

703
00:32:32,860 --> 00:32:33,700
No.

704
00:32:33,780 --> 00:32:35,740
No, not at all.

705
00:32:37,220 --> 00:32:38,260
Before I lost my memory,

706
00:32:38,260 --> 00:32:39,700
I did know her, right?

707
00:32:39,700 --> 00:32:40,540
No.

708
00:32:41,460 --> 00:32:42,300
No.

709
00:32:44,220 --> 00:32:45,740
What could make

710
00:32:45,740 --> 00:32:46,700
two women

711
00:32:46,700 --> 00:32:48,500
so antagonistic?

712
00:32:51,620 --> 00:32:52,540
Could it be

713
00:32:53,340 --> 00:32:55,020
she's the mistress of my husband?

714
00:32:55,020 --> 00:32:55,860
She...

715
00:32:56,500 --> 00:32:57,340
She...

716
00:32:58,500 --> 00:32:59,540
She is

717
00:33:00,460 --> 00:33:02,060
your adulterer's mistress.

718
00:33:08,100 --> 00:33:09,860
What a sin.

719
00:33:13,820 --> 00:33:15,940
(Mansion of Lord Huaiyang)

720
00:33:26,300 --> 00:33:33,300
(Mansion of Lord Huaiyang)

721
00:33:51,500 --> 00:33:52,340
Madam.

722
00:33:53,500 --> 00:33:54,380
Have some tea.

723
00:33:58,150 --> 00:34:00,580
As for the adulterer,

724
00:34:01,360 --> 00:34:03,100
the master has put it behind.

725
00:34:03,250 --> 00:34:04,090
Madam,

726
00:34:04,190 --> 00:34:05,380
no need not worry further.

727
00:34:06,970 --> 00:34:08,740
No wonder Sun Yun'er came to bother me.

728
00:34:09,440 --> 00:34:10,920
It's all due to the entanglement.

729
00:34:12,160 --> 00:34:13,380
But I see Ziyu

730
00:34:13,380 --> 00:34:14,700
is also not a good person,

731
00:34:14,700 --> 00:34:15,900
fickle and unreliable,

732
00:34:16,580 --> 00:34:17,840
much worse than my husband.

733
00:34:19,220 --> 00:34:20,060
Indeed.

734
00:34:20,260 --> 00:34:21,100
Nanny Li,

735
00:34:21,860 --> 00:34:23,140
have you seen

736
00:34:23,140 --> 00:34:24,460
our marriage certificate?

737
00:34:27,140 --> 00:34:27,980
Well.

738
00:34:31,500 --> 00:34:33,580
Only the master and you know

739
00:34:33,580 --> 00:34:36,180
where the marriage certificate is stored.

740
00:34:36,180 --> 00:34:37,020
I never

741
00:34:37,100 --> 00:34:38,660
touch it.

742
00:34:39,020 --> 00:34:40,860
I searched every room,

743
00:34:41,260 --> 00:34:42,900
only finding property deeds and drafts,

744
00:34:43,060 --> 00:34:44,380
not the marriage certificate.

745
00:34:44,820 --> 00:34:45,780
Could it be

746
00:34:45,780 --> 00:34:47,260
someone else took it?

747
00:34:48,660 --> 00:34:49,500
Madam,

748
00:34:49,820 --> 00:34:50,660
I confess

749
00:34:51,220 --> 00:34:53,020
my mistake.

750
00:34:53,380 --> 00:34:54,220
Confess?

751
00:34:54,620 --> 00:34:56,940
When we moved from the capital,

752
00:34:56,940 --> 00:34:58,380
I was busy dismissing servants

753
00:34:58,380 --> 00:34:59,540
and selling property.

754
00:34:59,740 --> 00:35:01,980
All the household affairs

755
00:35:02,140 --> 00:35:04,140
were managed by me alone.

756
00:35:04,380 --> 00:35:05,700
So I

757
00:35:06,380 --> 00:35:08,740
was overwhelmed

758
00:35:08,740 --> 00:35:10,660
and lost the marriage certificate.

759
00:35:12,260 --> 00:35:13,540
I lost it.

760
00:35:13,980 --> 00:35:14,900
Lost it?

761
00:35:14,900 --> 00:35:16,740
It's my fault for being careless

762
00:35:16,740 --> 00:35:18,260
so as to lose such an important item.

763
00:35:18,260 --> 00:35:20,460
I cannot atone for my mistake.

764
00:35:20,460 --> 00:35:23,220
Sorry to the master and you, Madam.

765
00:35:24,140 --> 00:35:25,340
It's lost, so be it.

766
00:35:25,620 --> 00:35:26,660
Nanny Li, please rise.

767
00:35:28,940 --> 00:35:30,020
Thank you, Madam.

768
00:35:30,020 --> 00:35:30,860
Losing the certificate

769
00:35:30,860 --> 00:35:32,700
doesn't make the marriage fake.

770
00:35:38,180 --> 00:35:40,700
(Draft)

771
00:35:41,860 --> 00:35:43,860
(Deed)

772
00:35:44,300 --> 00:35:45,700
We'll end here for today.

773
00:35:46,140 --> 00:35:46,980
You may leave.

774
00:35:49,460 --> 00:35:50,460
My Lord,

775
00:35:50,460 --> 00:35:52,460
we shall take our leave.

776
00:35:54,900 --> 00:35:55,740
Miss He.

777
00:35:56,620 --> 00:35:57,460
Please stay.

778
00:36:04,940 --> 00:36:07,020
I heard your father is unwell.

779
00:36:07,580 --> 00:36:08,860
Thank you for your concern.

780
00:36:09,060 --> 00:36:10,220
My father is bedridden,

781
00:36:10,300 --> 00:36:11,780
so I am handling affairs for him.

782
00:36:12,420 --> 00:36:13,780
But did you know

783
00:36:15,050 --> 00:36:17,540
your father sent a letter saying your family

784
00:36:17,540 --> 00:36:18,900
would be absent today?

785
00:36:20,700 --> 00:36:22,140
It was my decision to come here.

786
00:36:22,300 --> 00:36:23,380
Please forgive me, My Lord.

787
00:36:23,500 --> 00:36:24,700
There's no need to apologize.

788
00:36:25,700 --> 00:36:27,060
I know why you're here.

789
00:36:28,740 --> 00:36:30,420
I recently heard

790
00:36:30,420 --> 00:36:31,460
some rumors.

791
00:36:31,740 --> 00:36:33,540
Upon reflection,

792
00:36:35,220 --> 00:36:36,300
I realized

793
00:36:36,300 --> 00:36:37,540
I too have made mistakes,

794
00:36:38,060 --> 00:36:39,420
which caused you

795
00:36:39,660 --> 00:36:40,860
to suffer unjustly.

796
00:36:41,660 --> 00:36:43,060
We met today.

797
00:36:43,180 --> 00:36:45,420
I must apologize to you.

798
00:36:49,260 --> 00:36:50,300
This matter

799
00:36:50,700 --> 00:36:52,300
was indeed caused by me.

800
00:36:53,060 --> 00:36:54,420
With your wedding approaching,

801
00:36:54,940 --> 00:36:56,580
I should not trouble you any further.

802
00:36:57,780 --> 00:36:59,260
I only have

803
00:36:59,260 --> 00:37:00,540
one daring question to ask.

804
00:37:04,740 --> 00:37:05,820
Did you reject me

805
00:37:06,380 --> 00:37:08,420
because I come from a merchant family?

806
00:37:08,900 --> 00:37:09,820
I absolutely do not

807
00:37:09,820 --> 00:37:11,100
look down on you.

808
00:37:11,420 --> 00:37:13,260
Was it because Ms. Lian refused to accept me?

809
00:37:16,180 --> 00:37:17,500
I am a stranger to you.

810
00:37:18,260 --> 00:37:20,700
If I let you be my concubine,

811
00:37:21,340 --> 00:37:22,500
it would be unfair to you.

812
00:37:25,340 --> 00:37:26,820
What if I'm willing

813
00:37:27,860 --> 00:37:29,180
and wouldn't feel wronged?

814
00:37:31,300 --> 00:37:33,580
If I took you in,

815
00:37:34,860 --> 00:37:35,980
you should know

816
00:37:36,620 --> 00:37:38,500
I wouldn't devote myself wholly to you,

817
00:37:39,100 --> 00:37:40,660
and you wouldn't want to share

818
00:37:40,660 --> 00:37:41,700
your husband with others.

819
00:37:42,940 --> 00:37:44,020
In that case,

820
00:37:45,500 --> 00:37:47,060
you'd only end up with regrets.

821
00:37:47,060 --> 00:37:48,700
Even with high status and wealth,

822
00:37:49,100 --> 00:37:50,500
you'd only experience pain,

823
00:37:50,500 --> 00:37:51,340
leading

824
00:37:52,700 --> 00:37:54,060
to estrangement.

825
00:37:58,580 --> 00:38:00,580
You're so considerate of women.

826
00:38:01,100 --> 00:38:02,700
You must have someone you love.

827
00:38:04,140 --> 00:38:05,940
Thank you for enlightening me today.

828
00:38:23,740 --> 00:38:24,940
Someone I love?

829
00:38:26,380 --> 00:38:27,220
Do I?

830
00:38:28,100 --> 00:38:33,460
(Mansion of Lord Huaiyang)

831
00:38:40,860 --> 00:38:42,420
Miss, are you going back home?

832
00:38:43,420 --> 00:38:44,260
No.

833
00:38:44,380 --> 00:38:45,340
Go to North Street.

834
00:38:45,660 --> 00:38:47,180
I want to tell Ms. Liu

835
00:38:47,820 --> 00:38:48,700
that I've let go.

836
00:39:05,860 --> 00:39:08,300
(Cui Mansion)

837
00:39:10,820 --> 00:39:11,660
Master?

838
00:39:23,620 --> 00:39:24,460
Honey.

839
00:39:38,260 --> 00:39:39,220
You're back.

840
00:39:41,660 --> 00:39:42,500
Come on.

841
00:39:43,180 --> 00:39:44,260
Sit with me for a while.

842
00:39:45,590 --> 00:39:51,760
♪The boat drifts, bringing back the sunset♪

843
00:39:52,720 --> 00:39:59,000
♪When we reunite, we still joke
about the cause and effect♪

844
00:40:01,180 --> 00:40:02,860
If you keep looking like that,

845
00:40:03,100 --> 00:40:04,460
will your gaze burn a hole

846
00:40:04,460 --> 00:40:05,340
in me?

847
00:40:09,260 --> 00:40:10,100
Dear.

848
00:40:13,020 --> 00:40:14,140
I have some

849
00:40:14,500 --> 00:40:15,860
good news to tell you.

850
00:40:16,180 --> 00:40:17,060
Coincidentally,

851
00:40:17,180 --> 00:40:18,340
I also have some good news

852
00:40:18,340 --> 00:40:19,300
to share with you.

853
00:40:19,300 --> 00:40:20,180
Then you go first.

854
00:40:20,340 --> 00:40:22,220
Don't get too carried away with joy.

855
00:40:22,220 --> 00:40:23,060
Alright.

856
00:40:24,220 --> 00:40:26,260
Lord Huaiyang is getting married this month.

857
00:40:26,340 --> 00:40:28,300
According to customs, the business chamber

858
00:40:28,300 --> 00:40:29,620
needs to prepare the porcelain.

859
00:40:29,980 --> 00:40:31,340
Our Yushao Porcelain Shop

860
00:40:31,340 --> 00:40:32,620
has gained certification.

861
00:40:33,220 --> 00:40:35,900
Honey, our porcelain
can enter the Lord's mansion.

862
00:40:36,620 --> 00:40:38,860
Perhaps on the wedding day,

863
00:40:39,020 --> 00:40:40,900
the Lord will drink with his wife

864
00:40:41,020 --> 00:40:42,860
from the cups we made.

865
00:40:58,220 --> 00:41:00,140
I knew you'd get carried away with joy.

866
00:41:02,820 --> 00:41:04,060
Indeed, I am delighted.

867
00:41:05,220 --> 00:41:06,060
Dear,

868
00:41:06,740 --> 00:41:07,940
I need to tell you

869
00:41:08,500 --> 00:41:10,020
that the teacher said I've recently

870
00:41:10,780 --> 00:41:11,860
improved in Go skills.

871
00:41:12,260 --> 00:41:14,460
Since I couldn't learn much in the club,

872
00:41:14,460 --> 00:41:16,060
he introduced me to a national master

873
00:41:16,340 --> 00:41:17,180
and asked me to go

874
00:41:17,300 --> 00:41:18,180
to study under him.

875
00:41:18,300 --> 00:41:19,180
Really?

876
00:41:20,100 --> 00:41:20,940
So,

877
00:41:21,060 --> 00:41:23,020
this is a double happiness.

878
00:41:23,020 --> 00:41:23,940
I'll go get ready.

879
00:41:24,980 --> 00:41:25,820
Dear,

880
00:41:27,740 --> 00:41:29,700
but this time the teacher said

881
00:41:30,500 --> 00:41:31,340
I can't

882
00:41:32,100 --> 00:41:33,260
bring my family.

883
00:41:41,180 --> 00:41:42,020
Well.

884
00:41:42,860 --> 00:41:44,580
When are you leaving?

885
00:41:46,460 --> 00:41:47,300
Well.

886
00:41:48,540 --> 00:41:49,740
Tonight.

887
00:41:49,940 --> 00:41:51,060
So soon?

888
00:41:52,100 --> 00:41:53,260
Such opportunities are rare.

889
00:41:53,700 --> 00:41:54,940
I've already asked Moru

890
00:41:54,940 --> 00:41:56,220
to help me pack.

891
00:41:58,980 --> 00:42:00,580
When will you return?

892
00:42:03,380 --> 00:42:04,500
Maybe in a month.

893
00:42:04,500 --> 00:42:05,460
Maybe...

894
00:42:07,100 --> 00:42:07,940
Dear,

895
00:42:09,660 --> 00:42:11,820
don't you want to eat the dishes
from your hometown?

896
00:42:12,180 --> 00:42:13,460
It's a good chance

897
00:42:14,020 --> 00:42:14,940
to go back for a visit.

898
00:42:18,180 --> 00:42:19,420
You look guilty.

899
00:42:23,940 --> 00:42:25,220
Every time you leave,

900
00:42:25,740 --> 00:42:26,980
you're always in such a hurry.

901
00:42:27,860 --> 00:42:29,420
As your wife,

902
00:42:29,900 --> 00:42:31,940
I never have time to prepare anything.

903
00:42:38,340 --> 00:42:39,580
Prepare what?

904
00:42:40,340 --> 00:42:41,380
Remember

905
00:42:43,060 --> 00:42:44,140
to take

906
00:42:44,140 --> 00:42:45,220
the medicine patches.

907
00:42:46,420 --> 00:42:47,980
Keep them warm in front of the fire

908
00:42:48,820 --> 00:42:49,700
each night

909
00:42:50,140 --> 00:42:52,020
before you apply them to your arms.

910
00:42:53,860 --> 00:42:54,940
After two months,

911
00:42:56,660 --> 00:42:57,660
you will be recovered.

912
00:43:00,620 --> 00:43:02,060
When you meet the master,

913
00:43:02,180 --> 00:43:03,540
you must attend to formalities.

914
00:43:03,980 --> 00:43:05,660
If you need anything,

915
00:43:05,660 --> 00:43:06,780
just send a message.

916
00:43:06,860 --> 00:43:08,460
I'll have Nanny Li deliver it to you.

917
00:43:10,140 --> 00:43:13,100
Also, the mountain can be very cold.

918
00:43:13,580 --> 00:43:15,020
You like cold drinks and wearing

919
00:43:15,500 --> 00:43:17,180
light clothes while practicing boxing.

920
00:43:17,580 --> 00:43:18,740
When you're warm,

921
00:43:18,740 --> 00:43:20,180
don't indulge in the cold.

922
00:43:26,020 --> 00:43:27,300
Moru can handle

923
00:43:28,860 --> 00:43:29,740
these trivial matters.

924
00:43:30,180 --> 00:43:31,260
You needn't worry.

925
00:43:39,500 --> 00:43:40,380
I'll leave now.

926
00:43:41,700 --> 00:43:42,540
Goodbye.

927
00:44:07,340 --> 00:44:13,570
♪The boat drifts,
bringing back the sunset♪

928
00:44:14,570 --> 00:44:20,690
♪When we reunite, we still joke
about the cause and effect♪

929
00:44:21,680 --> 00:44:27,930
♪Who passed by, the crabapple
falls with a turn♪

930
00:44:29,060 --> 00:44:32,300
♪Loving rightly but choosing wrong♪

931
00:44:32,640 --> 00:44:37,220
♪With joys, sorrows, partings and reunions♪

932
00:44:37,820 --> 00:44:44,480
♪Everyone travels far, seeing clouds and snow♪

933
00:44:45,230 --> 00:44:48,600
♪Always hard to stay, yet easy to part♪

934
00:44:48,890 --> 00:44:52,220
♪Crossing spring waters and autumn trials♪

935
00:44:52,400 --> 00:44:59,170
♪A couple under the moonlight,
can stay together♪

936
00:44:59,550 --> 00:45:06,320
♪Long hidden in the eyes,
flickering in and out♪

937
00:45:06,820 --> 00:45:13,230
♪Let go of the flowers blooming
in the yard last night♪

938
00:45:14,070 --> 00:45:20,480
♪Let go of the waves in the stream
in half a lifetime♪

939
00:45:21,060 --> 00:45:27,680
♪Let those dust and chaos go on endlessly♪

940
00:45:28,480 --> 00:45:31,900
♪In this lifetime, my wish is to the vast sky♪

941
00:45:31,900 --> 00:45:37,000
♪There are many more♪

942
00:45:37,380 --> 00:45:44,100
♪Everyone travels far, seeing clouds and snow♪

943
00:45:44,670 --> 00:45:48,300
♪Always hard to stay, yet easy to part♪

944
00:45:48,300 --> 00:45:51,700
♪Crossing spring waters and autumn trials♪

945
00:45:51,700 --> 00:45:58,610
♪A couple under the moonlight,
can stay together♪

946
00:45:58,900 --> 00:46:05,750
♪Time flows as we dream through four seasons♪

947
00:46:06,120 --> 00:46:09,700
♪I wish to journey with you forever♪

948
00:46:09,700 --> 00:46:12,810
♪Year after year♪

949
00:46:14,540 --> 00:46:18,840
♪For many years to come♪
